<HEADLINE>
<P>
CURRENTS: A GUIDE TO THE BEST OF SOUTHERN CALIFORNIA; 
</P>
<P>
MAPS; 
</P>
<P>
THE 3-D EFFECT 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By KARRE SLAFKIN 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
UPON first glimpse of a Raven oversized detailed wall map, many people run 
their fingers across the surface to prove to themselves that it's not a raised 
relief. 
</P>
<P>
The digital landscapes, a unique combination of relief shading and elevation 
tinting, have a 3-D effect. The maps run from $20 to $65. 
</P>
<P>
 Raven Maps are sold at Geographia, 4000 Riverside Drive, Burbank; (818) 
848-1414. Or telephone (800) 237-0798. 
</P>
<P>
KARRE SLAFKIN 
</P>
</TEXT>
<GRAPHIC>
<P>
Photo, COLOR, map Juan Lopez 
