<HEADLINE>
<P>
WRONG TIME 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Concerning the Aug. 19 interview with rock musician Bob Geldof: Samuel Pepys 
lived during the Restoration period in England, not the Reformation (as Geldof 
was quoted as saying). 
</P>
<P>
The two periods were about 130 years apart: 1529 marked the beginning of the 
Reformation; 1660, the Restoration. 
</P>
<P>
KIM THORNTON 
</P>
<P>
Lake Forest 
</P>
