to leave for Camp Pendleton from Los Angeles. DAVID RAE MORRIS / Los Angeles 
Times; Photo, Reservists Robin Neel, left, and Pamela Collins have an 
unexpected reunion in front of the Naval and Marine Corps Reserve Center in San 
Diego, where both arrived Saturday to report for duty. DAVID MC NEW / Los 
Angeles Times; Photo, (Orange County Edition) COLOR, Reservists practice 
beach-landing skills in amphibious cargo vessel on Camp Pendleton's Red Beach. 
