<HEADLINE>
<P>
ENROLLMENT OPENS FOR YWCA CHILD CARE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The YWCA of the Harbor Area is now accepting enrollment for its after-school 
child-care program. 
</P>
<P>
The state-licensed program is designed to meet the needs of kindergarten and 
elementary children of working parents. It includes pickup at selected San 
Pedro schools, time and assistance with homework, games, crafts, trips and 
snacks. The program operates from 11 a.m. to 6 p.m. Monday through Friday 
during the school year. The cost is $40 a week for each child and a $40 
registration fee. For information call 547-0831. 
</P>
</TEXT>
