</P>
</TYPE>
<SUBJECT>
<P>
LITTLE LEAGUE BASEBALL; LITTLE LEAGUE WORLD SERIES; CYPRESS (CA) -- ATHLETICS; 
BASEBALL TEAMS 
</P>
